    </p>

    \[\cos({3\pi\over 2}-\alpha) = \cos{3\pi\over 2}\cos\alpha + \sin{3\pi\over 2}\sin\alpha = 0\cos\alpha + (-1)\sin\alpha= -\sin\alpha\]

