    \[\cos(-{4\pi\over 3}) = - \sqrt{1-\sin^2\left(-{4\pi\over 3}\right)} = - \sqrt{1-\left({\sqrt{3}\over 2}\right)^2} = - \sqrt{1-{3\over 4}}=-{1\over 2}\]

